<br />It's been my experience living and working in Japan that the Japanese love to produce documents.  The office culture here pressures you to "always appear busy even if you have nothing to do".  The result is a surplus of documents.  I'm being half-silly, but it's a little true.  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

